description: Most of the world uses the very logical metric system and thus for them the English system used in the US is totally random and illogical. This skill will give various measurement relationships used in the English system.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask English System to tell me a fact.
Alexa, ask English System to tell me something.
Alexa, ask English System to tell me trivia.
name: english system
shortDescription: The skill will give facts about the English measurement system.
